body:
I&#039;m starting to think the bots that are not infesting ARAM are not even being worked on. If anything I feel like they bots are just getting their AI worked on. What would be a GREAT help is if the bots, ALL OF THEM, were removed entirely. I don&#039;t even want to play ARAM anymore due to the bots being an issue. I&#039;ve even noticed some bots are getting through classic matches as well. I understand we want to get into a match as fast as possible BUT filling it with bots is NOT the way to go.{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 
I really hope this issue gets resolved... I used to have fun playing ARAM not its just annoying...
Riot I hope you are doing what the community wants. Some people are starting to think you guys created those bots just to try and satisfy those who hate waiting to get into a match{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}
